## Managing Libraries

```bash
pixi add packagename              # add from conda
pixi add --pypi packagename       # add from PyPI
pixi remove packagename           # remove
pixi list                         # list all installed
```

## Tasks

```bash
pixi run setup                    # register Python kernel
{{if eq .DocSystem "quarto"}}
pixi run render                   # render report to PDF
{{else if eq .DocSystem "myst"}}
pixi run docs-start               # live-preview MyST site
pixi run docs-build               # build MyST HTML site
pixi run docs-pdf                 # export report to PDF
pixi run docs-clean               # clean build artifacts
{{end}}
pixi run marimo file.py           # edit Marimo notebook
pixi run kernels                  # list registered kernels
```
{{else}}
## Managing Libraries

```bash
uv add packagename                # add a package
uv remove packagename             # remove a package
uv pip list                       # list all installed
uv sync                           # sync from lockfile
```

## Tasks

```bash
uv run poe setup                  # register Python kernel
{{if eq .DocSystem "quarto"}}
uv run poe render                 # render report to PDF
{{else if eq .DocSystem "myst"}}
uv run poe docs-start             # live-preview MyST site
uv run poe docs-build             # build MyST HTML site
uv run poe docs-pdf               # export report to PDF
uv run poe docs-clean             # clean build artifacts
{{end}}
uv run poe marimo file.py         # edit Marimo notebook
uv run poe kernels                # list registered kernels
uv run poe update                 # refresh packages
```
{{end}}
